  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, combine the grated carrots, beets, and radishes. ",
    "Add the thinly sliced onion and chopped fresh dill to the bowl. ",
    "In a separate bowl, mix the apple cider vinegar with water. ",
    "Add the kosher salt, granulated sugar, and sodium alginate to the vinegar mixture. ",
    "Add the citric acid to the vinegar mixture and stir well. ",
    "Slowly pour the vinegar mixture into a pitcher of cold water while stirring constantly. ",
    "Continue stirring the mixture until spheres start to form. ",
    "Use a siphon to carefully extract the spheres and place them in the bowl with the vegetables. "
  ],
